@node History

                             Password History
                             ================

Important  notice:  If you are upgrading from an older release of Password,
make  sure you remove the OLD Password with the OLD RemovePassword-program.
You  cannot  combine programs from different releases, i.e.  RemovePassword
V1.1 will NOT recognize Passwords installed with InstallPassword V1.0!!!

V1.0   (25.02.93)   First public release

V1.1   (26.04.93)   · Looks for the RigidDiskBlock within the
                      RDB_LOCATION_LIMIT.
                    · Should now properly preserve 'FILL' blocks. Those
                      blocks are not documented in devices/hardblocks.h
                      (as of V39), so V1.0 didn't recognize them. They
                      still might not be properly supported. Password
                      simply won't touch any blocks of type 'FILL'.
                      Thanks to Martin Berndt for telling me about
                      those blocks.

@endnode
